{"tid":1509042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非呀和理非，說好的大三罷呢？？？","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:27:29.000Z","uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3561edbcca4447ac9846dcb0184b94d6b0c7947f","tid":1509042,"uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"轉載Pokemon Go HK Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1347755002070986?sfns=cl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F596896340490193%2Fposts%2F1347755002070986%3Fsfns%3Dcl&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=4d989146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1347755002070986?sfns=cl</a><br />\n<br />\n每一件事，都不能忘記：<br />\n<br />\n七位義士以死相諫，佢哋嘅家人要永久傷痛。<br />\n<br />\n超過 700人被捕，當中有好多係少女、細路、街坊。<br />\n<br />\n近半百人被控最重嘅暴動罪，刑期十年。<br />\n<br />\n起碼有三十人被差佬喺差館打到骨折、重傷。部份人有可能會終身殘廢。<br />\n<br />\n有少女指證差佬迫佢全裸搜身，期間有好多男警做觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n最少五人被子彈打中頭部，當中兩位已失明。<br />\n<br />\n起碼有一個人被黑社會打到終身傷殘，另外多人重傷。警察事前視而不見，事後求其拉幾個當交數。<br />\n<br />\n示威期間，差佬多次對已被制服嘅市民拳打腳踢。當中多次用武器發洩式咁毆打示威者，特別係打女仔嗰陣。<br />\n<br />\n警察亦多次被影到用真槍實彈，以水平角度射向市民。事後嘅記者會，死都要話自己係射地下。指鹿為馬。<br />\n<br />\n多名白衫差佬被影到對黑社會客客氣氣，包括拍膊頭傾計、護送佢哋離開。而對記者同市民就呼呼喝喝，例如鬧示威者做「曱甴」。<br />\n<br />\n差佬多次以暴力對待和平示威嘅群眾。例如「觀星筆」事件，義憤嘅街坊只係企喺差館門口要求交待。警察就出防暴拉咗好多深水埗嘅居民。<br />\n<br />\n差佬亦製造白色恐怖。例如老屈個學生藏有攻擊性武器、拘捕網上媒體嘅管理員、入大學拉學生等等。<br />\n<br />\n區區放催淚毒煙，好多老人家同貓貓狗狗因此而得重病。<br />\n<br />\n每次記者會，政府都係話市民錯曬，佢自己就一樣機無錯。五大訴求，林鄭 tell the dog &mdash; 話狗知你班香港人！<br />\n<br />\n每一件事，都不能忘記<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非呀和理非，而家成八百個手足比狗拉左啦，仲坐係冷氣房睇電視，plan 下一次旅行去邊？ 說好的用經濟手段向政府施壓呢？等得黎香港都蚊瞓啦，唔係十二碎o既小朋友都唔洗上前線比人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非站在同一戰線方能發揮最大的威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠不割蓆，不篤灰，在前線的替我們擋子彈，在後方的為大家罷工，香港人加油！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他Ching 三罷post<br />\n馬路天使：［真係攬炒咩］升級大三罷，九月百萬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481216</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"46ee81a41a533523d53ba0889a496e40cc634cc2","tid":1509042,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=80b3bb21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=e9b3ee8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1eb30348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"p